window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>To the Christian's in Rome, the Apostle Paul says \"I am eager to preach the gospel to you who are at Rome.\" (Romans 1:15). </p> <p>Evidently, Christians need to hear the gospel even after conversion: and <i>A Gospel Primer</i> for Christians is designed to help you do just that. By showing how you can preach the gospel to yourself each day, this book will help you savor the glories of God's love and experience the life-transforming power of the gospel in all areas of life. Use this book to preach the gospel to yourself on a daily basis, and be amazed at the differences it can make in your life.</p>"; 
